m/discussion/171267/we-got-dedicated\">We GOT DEDICATED.</a></p><p>Serveroffer.net has&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171275/serveroffer-net-5-eur-dedicated-server-hosting-offer-eu\">5 EUR dedicated servers.</a></p><p>NexusBytes offers some awfully&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171243/packed-with-delicious-bytes-to-fill-up-your-appetite-grab-em-while-hot-us-nl-uk-sg-jp\">delicious Bytes in US|NL|UK|SG|JP</a>.</p><p>Reprise Hosting has dedicated servers&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171268/dedicated-servers-starting-at-24-95-month-first-10-buyers-only-ipmi-double-ram-double-bw\">starting at $24.95/month</a>.</p><p>Terrahost announced that they\u2019re launching <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171253/terrahost-launches-1gbps-unmetered-dedicated-servers-in-norway\">1Gbps Unmetered Dedicated Servers in Norway</a>.</p><p>NetDyanmics24 offers <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171221/20-lifetime-discount-on-backup-storage-netdynamics24\">20% Lifetime Discount on Backup Storage</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171273/vpsnet-com-fast-ssd-vps-in-europe-from-2-25-1gb-ram-30-days-money-back\">VPSnet.com has Fast SSD VPS in Europe</a> from $2.25/mo</p><p>Looking for cheap cloud hosting?&nbsp; Check out <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171225/cloudjiffy-cloud-made-simple\">CloudJiffy</a>.</p><p>LeapSwitch has offers in <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171224/mumbai-india-usa-germany-portugal-spain-2gb-ram-1-core-30gb-ssd-5\">Mumbai, USA, Germany, Portugal, and Spain</a>.</p><p>VPSSLIM offers KVMs with <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171223/netherlands-pure-ssd-storage-kvm-vps-2-cores-4-gb-ram-150-ssd-7\">pure SSD storage and 4 GB RAM for $7</a></p><p>JustVPS has Singapore VMs starting at <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171202/cloud-vps-in-singapore-from-3-68-centos-debian-ubuntu-windows\">$3.68</a